commit_message:
Updating version to 0.75. 
This version fixes a mishandling of BWA multimapped reads.

Editing PotentialRegionFilter

Applying blacklist filter to entire chromosome before potential regions
are found. This brings MultiGPS potential region filtering in line with
ChExMix's approach.

Fix bug in MotifPlatform.java
Fixed bug where a random region could sometimes have a coordinate range
outside of the chromosome.
Adding .txt extension to differential files for Galaxy version.
Fixing some .txt extensions for Galaxy MultiGPS
Adjustments to v0.73 with option to enforce non-parallel MEME
dded support for full-genome FASTA files in --seq option
Changed version number to 0.72 to reflect move to new repo
Checked all parameters documented correctly in help.
adding lib directory to help eclipse imports
